<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Thiago F. Miranda</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/</link><description>Recent content on Thiago F. Miranda</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 11:06:25 +0600</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Machine Learning API Test</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/posts/projects/teste-api/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 11:06:25 +0600</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/posts/projects/teste-api/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="introduction">Introduction&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>I decided to write this post to demonstrate how to test my ML API deployed on AWS, you may find the API project in my repository: &lt;a href="https://github.com/thiagofmiranda/machine-learning-aws-api" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Machine Learning AWS API&lt;/a>. This project aims to create a Python API using FastAPI and deploy it to AWS Lambda. The API is designed to serve predictions based on models imported from an external repository: &lt;a href="https://github.com/thiagofmiranda/machine-learning-models" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Machine Learning Models Repository&lt;/a>. The application is containerized with Docker, providing an isolated and reproducible development environment.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Introduction</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/posts/personal/about-me/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 11:06:25 +0600</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/posts/personal/about-me/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="about-me">About Me&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>Hi, Iâ€™m Thiago! ðŸ‘‹&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Iâ€™m a passionate &lt;strong>Data Scientist&lt;/strong> with over 6 years of experience in data analytics, machine learning, and statistical modeling. I specialize in building robust machine learning pipelines, automating processes, and delivering actionable insights that drive business decisions. My journey began with a strong foundation in &lt;strong>Statistics&lt;/strong>, which Iâ€™m further enhancing through my ongoing &lt;strong>Masterâ€™s degree&lt;/strong> at the University of SÃ£o Paulo, focusing on &lt;strong>Latent Trait Models&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Introduction</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/basic/introduction/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/basic/introduction/</guid><description>&lt;!-- A Sample Program -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Hello World&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;p>A sample Python program is shown here.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">def&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">greet&lt;/span>(name):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">f&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Hello, &lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">{&lt;/span>name&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">}&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">if&lt;/span> __name__ &lt;span style="color:#f92672">==&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> message &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> greet(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;world&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(message)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Run the program as below:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ python hello.py
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Introduction</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/basic/introduction/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/basic/introduction/</guid><description>&lt;!-- A Sample Program -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Hello World&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;p>A sample R program is shown here.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-R" data-lang="R">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>greet &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">function&lt;/span>(name) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">paste&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Hello,&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, name, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>message &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">greet&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;world&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(message)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Basic Types</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/basic/types/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/basic/types/</guid><description>&lt;!-- String Type -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Strings&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>str_single &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>str_multiline &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;Multiline
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">string&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>print(str_multiline&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>upper())
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Useful string methods:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>name &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;John Doe&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>print(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>lower()) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># john doe&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>print(name&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>split()) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># [&amp;#39;John&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;Doe&amp;#39;]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;!-- Number Types -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Numbers&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>integer &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">42&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>floating_point &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3.14&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>complex_number &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">+&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3&lt;/span>j
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Converting between types&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>float_to_int &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> int(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3.7&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 3&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Working with NumPy for advanced number manipulation:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">import&lt;/span> numpy &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">as&lt;/span> np
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>array &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> np&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>array([&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3&lt;/span>])
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>print(array&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>mean()) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 2.0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Basic Types</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/basic/types/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/basic/types/</guid><description>&lt;!-- String Type -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Strings&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>str_single &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>str_multiline &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Multiline\nstring&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">toupper&lt;/span>(str_multiline)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Useful string manipulation with &lt;code>stringr&lt;/code>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">library&lt;/span>(stringr)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>name &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;John Doe&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">str_to_lower&lt;/span>(name) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># &amp;#34;john doe&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">str_split&lt;/span>(name, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34; &amp;#34;&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># List of &amp;#34;John&amp;#34; and &amp;#34;Doe&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;!-- Number Types -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Numbers&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>integer &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">42L&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>floating_point &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3.14&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>complex_number &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">complex&lt;/span>(real &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>, imaginary &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Converting between types&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>float_to_int &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">as.integer&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3.7&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 3&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Working with vectors:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>nums &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">c&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">3&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">4&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">5&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">mean&lt;/span>(nums) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 3&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">sum&lt;/span>(nums) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 15&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Flow Control</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/basic/flow-control/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/basic/flow-control/</guid><description>&lt;!-- Condition -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Condition&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>day &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;sunday&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">if&lt;/span> day &lt;span style="color:#f92672">in&lt;/span> [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;sunday&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;saturday&amp;#34;&lt;/span>]:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Rest!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">elif&lt;/span> day &lt;span style="color:#f92672">==&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;monday&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">and&lt;/span> is_tired():
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Groan!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">else&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Work!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Example with try/except:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">try&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> result &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">10&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">/&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">except&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">ZeroDivisionError&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Cannot divide by zero!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">finally&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Cleanup complete.&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;!-- Loops -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Loops&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;p>For loop example:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">for&lt;/span> i &lt;span style="color:#f92672">in&lt;/span> range(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">5&lt;/span>):
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">f&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Iteration &lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">{&lt;/span>i&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">}&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>While loop example:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>count &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">while&lt;/span> count &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">5&lt;/span>:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">f&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Count is &lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">{&lt;/span>count&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">}&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> count &lt;span style="color:#f92672">+=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Flow Control</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/basic/flow-control/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/basic/flow-control/</guid><description>&lt;!-- Condition -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Condition&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>day &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;sunday&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">if&lt;/span> (day &lt;span style="color:#f92672">%in%&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">c&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;sunday&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;saturday&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Rest!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">else&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">if&lt;/span> (day &lt;span style="color:#f92672">==&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;monday&amp;#34;&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Groan!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">else&lt;/span> {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Work!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Using &lt;code>tryCatch&lt;/code> for error handling:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>result &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">tryCatch&lt;/span>({
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">10&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">/&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}, warning &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">function&lt;/span>(w) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Warning occurred!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}, error &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">function&lt;/span>(e) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Error occurred!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}, finally &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Cleanup complete.&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>})
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(result)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;!-- Loops -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Loops&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;p>For loop example:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">for&lt;/span> (i &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">in&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">:&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">5&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">paste&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Iteration&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, i))
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>While loop example:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>count &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">0&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">while&lt;/span> (count &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">5&lt;/span>) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">paste&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Count is&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, count))
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> count &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> count &lt;span style="color:#f92672">+&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>File Manipulation</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/advanced/file-manipulation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/python/advanced/file-manipulation/</guid><description>&lt;!-- File Operations -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>File Operations&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;p>Reading and writing text files:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">with&lt;/span> open(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;example.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;w&amp;#34;&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">as&lt;/span> file:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> file&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>write(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Hello, File!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">with&lt;/span> open(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;example.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;r&amp;#34;&lt;/span>) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">as&lt;/span> file:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> content &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> file&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>read()
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> print(content)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Handling CSV files with pandas:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">import&lt;/span> pandas &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">as&lt;/span> pd
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Reading a CSV file&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>data &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> pd&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>read_csv(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;data.csv&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>print(data&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>head())
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Writing a CSV file&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>data&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>to_csv(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;output.csv&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, index&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">False&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>File Manipulation</title><link>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/advanced/file-manipulation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thiagofmiranda.com/notes/r/advanced/file-manipulation/</guid><description>&lt;!-- File Operations -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>File Operations&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;p>Reading and writing text files:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Writing to a file&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">writeLines&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Hello, File!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;example.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Reading from a file&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>content &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">readLines&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;example.txt&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(content)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Handling CSV files:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Reading a CSV file&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>data &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">read.csv&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;data.csv&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">head&lt;/span>(data)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Writing a CSV file&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">write.csv&lt;/span>(data, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;output.csv&amp;#34;&lt;/span>, row.names &lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">FALSE&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Working with Excel files using &lt;code>readxl&lt;/code> and &lt;code>writexl&lt;/code>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">library&lt;/span>(readxl)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">library&lt;/span>(writexl)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Reading Excel&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>data &lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;lt;-&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">read_excel&lt;/span>(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;data.xlsx&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">print&lt;/span>(data)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># Writing Excel&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e">write_xlsx&lt;/span>(data, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;output.xlsx&amp;#34;&lt;/span>)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>